  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Embark on a Tasty Journey to Master Japanese Kana and Vocabulary!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Learn Japanese With Sushi</strong> is the ultimate beginner-friendly game that combines the excitement of Japanese conveyor sushi and gachapon culture with a fast, fun, and interactive approach to learning katakana, hiragana, and basic Japanese vocabulary—including kanji. Designed for PC, this pixel-style mini-game adventure is perfect for anyone looking to kickstart their Japanese learning journey in a vibrant, playful environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/b496909dd69043505d278776b029a2f9.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/b496909dd69043505d278776b029a2f9.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/b496909dd69043505d278776b029a2f9.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/f1f5854e550f7dd315e00e42933cfe31.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/f1f5854e550f7dd315e00e42933cfe31.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/f1f5854e550f7dd315e00e42933cfe31.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/ea9b0062fe09f39037a303cc1bd16c04.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/ea9b0062fe09f39037a303cc1bd16c04.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/ea9b0062fe09f39037a303cc1bd16c04.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🍣 <strong>Sushi-Inspired Mini-Games</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Conveyor Sushi Challenge</strong>: Identify katakana and hiragana on moving sushi by typing or pressing the correct romanization.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customer Orders</strong>: Match sushi with katakana or hiragana to spoken audio orders from customers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sushi Box Sorting</strong>: Pair sushi displaying kanji or katakana vocabulary with the correct sushi boxes featuring their meanings and visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gachapon Fun</strong>: Use coins to play the gachapon machine and unlock exciting new vocabulary.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/76104ef8045d1deaf74bba91268cd535.poster.avif?t=1758435900\" width=800 height=500 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/76104ef8045d1deaf74bba91268cd535.webm?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3319740/extras/76104ef8045d1deaf74bba91268cd535.mp4?t=1758435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖 <strong>Mnemonic Dictionary</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boost your kana learning with a built-in mnemonic dictionary, making it easier to associate sounds with kana through memorable imagery and stories.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏅 <strong>Vocabulary Levels for N5-N3 Learners</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose vocabulary levels ranging from <strong>N5 to N3</strong>, allowing players to tailor their learning experience and focus on vocabulary that matches their proficiency.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>Customizable Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the speed and difficulty to suit your learning pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select specific kana sets or vocabulary ranges to focus on.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎧 <strong>Interactive Audio</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hear authentic pronunciations for kana and vocabulary words.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to connect sounds with visuals for a stronger memory link.</p></li></ul>",
