8435900\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >📖 <strong>Mnemonic Dictionary</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boost your kana learning with a built-in mnemonic dictionary, making it easier to associate sounds with kana through memorable imagery and stories.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏅 <strong>Vocabulary Levels for N5-N3 Learners</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose vocabulary levels ranging from <strong>N5 to N3</strong>, allowing players to tailor their learning experience and focus on vocabulary that matches their proficiency.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎮 <strong>Customizable Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adjust the speed and difficulty to suit your learning pace.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select specific kana sets or vocabulary ranges to focus on.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎧 <strong>Interactive Audio</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hear authentic pronunciations for kana and vocabulary words.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn to connect sounds with visuals for a stronger memory link.</p></li></ul>",
